cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use PolicyArena, please cite it as below."
title: "PolicyArena: A Policy-Compliant Tool-Calling + RAG Agent with Statistics-First Evaluation"
abstract: >-
  A Qwen3-8B policy-compliant tool-calling and RAG agent for a Chinese enterprise service
  desk. QLoRA-SFT lifts held-out success_rate 53.1% -> 96.9% and grounding 25.0% -> 87.5%
  (paired bootstrap, Holm-Bonferroni corrected) with zero policy violations reaching the
  user, enforced by a deterministic policy gate. Includes CI-enforced data-leakage guards,
  a decomposed safety metric (policy-violation vs unsafe-selection), and an honest failure
  analysis of an unsafe-selection regression under a small-data SFT regime.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "Yue"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-06"
